result.name: Bridal Tea House Hotel

reviews.text: The room is kinda small. There was no bidet available. But nevertheless our stay was comfortable.

I totally recommend this place for a single traveler. The room was barely bigger than a closet. But that is to be expected. Two people cannot occupy it. Nevertheless the room was spotless and housekeeping came every day. Everything was in working order. MOST IMPORTANT for a westerner, the hotel has a restaurant. The food at this restaurant never caused me to get ill. It is safe and clean to eat, which allows you to go out and enjoy the city. My compliments to the chef, the Chinese food they serve is nearly gourmet.

Too small. Don't have space to open my suitcase. No space to put things. The servuce is not very good too. When we went into the room, we realised that the air-con was not working for all of the rooms we booked. The staff took quite a long time before helping us.
So good
Room is pretty small, but very convenient as it is near to train station. I like the tea smell of the lobby, should be tea fragrance... The hotel is clean.
